{
  "stem": "9728.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they came in, you know, the first, the, the first part, or the first of them-- the First Battalion of them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came on motorcycles, you know, with, with all the weapons and everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they marched through-- in Lodz, there was not much, not much people that they did confront them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Lodz, actually not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the bombing we heard, it was in, in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That they bombed Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in Lodz, I cannot remember that there was any bombing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe they flew over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe they dropped a bomb or two.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I cannot remember but that it should be a real bombing definitely.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "However, after several days they were in, they instituted what they called a sperre, that after 6 o'clock in the evening, no one is allowed to go on the street.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it was a curfew, something like a curfew, yes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At, at the first, we did not expect that they will be so militantly, and so anti-Semitic and so, so it-- that it will be so bad for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't expect-- maybe we were, we were too ignorant to know about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The thing that I remember first-- there was one incident.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I said before, we were, we sold our clothing on the market, on the fair, on Fridays.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was two or, about two or three weeks after the Germans arrived, and things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father went out in the morning, the early morning, with the-- to put the table on it, you know, to take his, his place and things.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he came back white, all completely white, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother asked him, what happened?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't ask.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't ask.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
